text: Roast duck, roast pork and char siew rice ($7.30) - the roast duck was tender and had crisp skin. The roast pork was fatty and particularly good. The char siew was fine. The duck broth was good.

Ordered roasted chicken and roasted pork takeaway, was charged that amount. But when i reached home, saw they did not add my roasted pork -.- went back to ask and they denied and even though i took pic of the receipt and food i received
taste is nice. just overlook the preparation method. long queues
Very Delicious and Cheap.Really recommend this place üëçüèª
